
1. All you should have to do is run the SQL script ./sql/db_schema and move the 
   contents of ./html into your web server's root directory.
2. sendmail needs to be installed for sending email to work. That's what the PHP 
   mail() function uses.
3. Database parameters are in ./html/database.php. The SQL script creates the 
   database and user to match what's currently in that file.
   
-Philip Westrich

